  "title": "Delivery Driver",
  "description": "<h4>Job Description</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide local delivery</li>\n  <li>Timely delivery of goods</li>\n  <li>Ensure that goods are delivered in good condition without delay or damages</li>\n  <li>Assist in loading and unloading of goods</li>\n  <li>Ensure cleanliness and maintenance of the delivery vehicle</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess class 3 &amp; 4 driving licence</li>\n  <li>Candidate with no experience are welcome as training will be provided</li>\n  <li>Preferably with 2 years local delivery experience with a 24 ft lorry (6 tonne)</li>\n  <li>Good safety records with zero traffic demerit points</li>\n</ul>",
